snippet.title: Skeletal Dance Party 💀 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/599160/Skeletal_Dance_Party/
https://catalopegames.itch.io/skeletal-dance-party
https://gamejolt.com/games/SkeletalDanceParty/335013
https://www.greenmangaming.com/games/skeletal-dance-party-pc/

Necromancers! Paladins! Skeletons! Monsters! Oh, my! You play as Reva, a young fox-eared necromancer who embarks on a quest to host an awesome dance party for all her friends… who happen to be the reanimated skeletons of her enemies along with some friendly monsters.

More information:
http://skeletaldance.party

Skeletal Dance Party is a collaboration between Catalope Games No Studio In Particular and several of our friends. Follow us here:
http://www.catalopegames.com/
https://twitter.com/CatalopeGames
https://www.facebook.com/CatalopeGames/

https://www.nostudioinparticular.com/

https://twitter.com/NSIPStudio
